               <head>Tafsir ha-Torah be-Farsit</head>
               <msContents class="lccn.loc.gov/n00020514">
                  <summary>Commentary on the Pentateuch in Judeo-Persian.</summary>
                  <textLang mainLang="jpr-Hebr" />
                  <msItem>
                     <locus from="1r" to="124v" />
                     <author />
                     <title xml:lang="he">תפסיר התורה בפרסית</title>
                     <title xml:lang="he-Latn-x-lc">Tafsir ha-Torah be-Farsit</title>
                     <incipit />
                     <msItem>
                        <locus from="1r" to="7r" />
                        <title>Genesis</title>
                        <note>
                           <p>Incomplete at the beginning.</p>
                           <p>Lacuna in the text between ff. 1v and 2r: f 1r: Parashat Lekh
                                        lekha (Gen. 12:1-17:27) - parashat Ṿa-yeraʾ (Gen.
                                        18:1-22:24); f. 2r: Parashat Ṿa-yetse Yaʿaḳov (Gen.
                                        28:10-32:3).</p>
                        </note>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem>
                        <locus from="7r" to="12v" />
                        <title>Exodus</title>
                        <note>
                           <p>From the end of Parashat Noah.</p>
                        </note>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem>
                        <locus from="13r" to="14r" />
                        <title>Leviticus</title>
                        <note>
                           <p>From Parashat Be-ḥuḳotai.</p>
                        </note>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem>
                        <locus from="14r" to="19v" />
                        <title>Numbers</title>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem>
                        <locus from="19v" to="27v" />
                        <title>Deuteronomy</title>
                        <note>
                           <p>Ff. 26r-28r copied by a different hand.</p>
                        </note>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem>
                        <locus from="28r" to="36r" />
                        <title>Ezekiel</title>
                     </msItem>
